--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 0.2.0 (2020-01-27)
F: Add optional configuration option to specify a comment per peer

* Version 0.1.4 (2020-01-03)
E: Minor template improvement (remove needless white space)

* Version 0.1.3 (2020-01-03)
E: Add optional configuration option to specify the server's PublicKey

* Version 0.1.2 (2020-01-03)
B: Add 'no_log' option to service tasks (Ansible output leaks private key)

* Version 0.1.1 (2020-01-03)
E: Define default state (enable) for config

* Version 0.1.0 (2020-01-02)
F: Initial release
